doses:
Hypertension, used alone, initially 12.5 mg twice daily;
if used in addition to diuretic (see notes above),
or in elderly, initially 6.25 mg twice daily (first dose at bedtime);
usual maintenance dose 25 mg twice daily; max. 50 mg twice daily (rarely
3 times daily in severe hypertension)

